flowchart LR
    subgraph REQ["One chat request"]
      Q[Query] --> CLS[Classify]
      CLS --> RW[Rewrite]
      RW --> RET[Retrieve contexts]
      RET --> GEN[Generate answer]
    end

    CLS -->|LiteLLM metadata trace_id| LF[Langfuse Trace]
    RW -->|LiteLLM metadata trace_id| LF
    GEN -->|tokens cost latency prompt response| LF

    GEN --> H[Layer 1 heuristic scoring]
    H --> H1[response_length]
    H --> H2[has_content]
    H --> H3[intent_confidence]
    H --> H4[source_count]
    H1 --> LF
    H2 --> LF
    H3 --> LF
    H4 --> LF

    GEN --> BG[Background evaluation thread]
    RET --> BG
    BG --> RAGAS{RAG path?}
    RAGAS -->|Yes| M1[RAGAS faithfulness]
    RAGAS -->|Yes| M2[RAGAS answer_relevancy]
    RAGAS -->|Yes| M3[RAGAS context_precision]
    RAGAS -->|Exact USER_SEARCH| J[LLM judge profile_relevance]
    M1 --> LF
    M2 --> LF
    M3 --> LF
    J --> LF

    UI[User feedback endpoint] --> UF[user_feedback score]
    UF --> LF
